## Ribozaimu - your digital all-purpose assistant!

This personal project is a small application with virtual pet that can currently track some of your activites and offers comments or remarks. All art done by me, code vibe-coded with ChatGPT - would not recommend, total mess and might have rewrite myself at some point. Also, plenty of redundant files that need to be removed.

### Current features
- speech upon startup
- close by double-clicking
- comments upon interaction with certain programs/windows such as Discord or Steam
- browser extension that can be installed to track activity on Twitter and YouTube

